The '''Patriarch''' was the title given to the leader of the [[Supreme Council of the Highland Clans]] that ruled the planet [[Skye/Legends|Skye]]. Such individuals would alternate between the [[Highland Clans|Highland]] and [[Lowland Clans]]. Once given the position, the clan would usually hold the position for forty-two years at which point they were required to hand the title to the other clan. [[Klarymére]] was the Patriarch of Skye until his [[Death/Legends|death]] during the [[Battle of Skye]], after which he was succeeded by one of his guardsmen, [[Aragh]].

